data.description: GOOAALLL! Hit the pitch & score on Midfield! This Parkway North Home is sure to be the MVP of your search. Attached 2 car garage & covered front porch as soon as you pull up to keep your whip & packages safe from the elements. Vaulted ceilings, crown molding & pristine hardwood floors once you’re inside. Cozy up by the fireplace while watching Ted Lasso. Entertain the entire team in the open living/dining room while you cook up something fresh for your squad in the updated kitchen with SS appliances, center island & granite countertops. Up the open staircase, you’ll find spacious bedrooms & plenty closet space including a primary suite & laundry room. Wanna watch the playoffs in style? The theater room in the finished basement is THE spot. Turn on the game while you smoke some meats on your private back deck. Community common ground to kick the ball around, clubhouse for big parties & pool to enjoy for next summer. Hurry up & score on Midfield before it’s too late! CHEERS!
